SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT DISTINCT ICPH_ADMNO, ICPH_CLNTNO, ICPH_BANKID, ICPH_BANKACCOUNT FROM :3/ICPH
--- 1 INNER JOIN :3/clnt ON CLNT101_ADMNO = ICPH_ADMNO AND CLNT102_CLNTNO = ICPH_CLNTNO AND CLNT212_INTERCREDIT = 'Y'
--- 2 INNER JOIN :3/CFLC ON ICPH_ADMNO=CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED AND ICPH_CLNTNO = CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED AND CFLC_USRID = ':2'
INNER JOIN :3/CLBD ON CLBD310_BANKID=ICPH_BANKID AND CLBD310_ADMNO=ICPH_BANK_ADMNO AND CLBD310_CLNTNO=ICPH_CLNTNO AND ICPH_ROWTYPE=1 AND ICPH_BOOKINGDATE>':1' AND ICPH_BANKACCOUNT <> '' AND CLBD310_BANKACCOUNT LIKE '%' || ICPH_BANKACCOUNT ||'%'
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
